+Decide whether Tao's tiny delayed trigger can be turned into one preferred exact-NS object that is concrete enough to support a smallest-faithful-support audit, or whether every honest formulation either collapses back to the already-killed five-role singleton circuit or relies on a non-canonical packet backup.
